---
// What We Do Section Component
---

<section class="what-we-do-section fix section-padding">
  <!-- Left Shape Image -->
  <div class="left-shape-image">
    <img src="/images/left-shape.png" alt="left shape">
  </div>
  <div class="container mxw-1450">
    <div class="what-we-wrapper">
      <div class="row g-4">
        <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".3s">
          <div class="thumb">
            <img src="/images/whatwedo.jpg" alt="img">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="what-we-content">
            <div class="section-title">
              <div class="subtitle wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".2s">
                What We Do 
                <img src="/images/fireIcon.svg" alt="icon">
              </div>
              <h2 class="title wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".4s">
                We connect the global and local sides of Vietnam’s game industry.
              </h2>
              <p class="wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".6s">
                There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but the majority have suffered alteration in some form
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="list-items-area">
              <div class="list-items wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".3s">
                <div class="icon">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="30" viewBox="0 0 26 30" fill="none">
                    <path d="M10.7219 1.19299C11.9737 0.456639 13.5263 0.456638 14.7781 1.19299L23.5281 6.34005C24.7498 7.05873 25.5 8.37033 25.5 9.78778V20.2122C25.5 21.6297 24.7498 22.9413 23.5281 23.66L14.7781 28.807C13.5263 29.5434 11.9737 29.5434 10.7219 28.807L1.97192 23.66C0.750167 22.9413 0 21.6297 0 20.2122V9.78778C0 8.37033 0.750165 7.05873 1.97192 6.34005L10.7219 1.19299Z" fill="#ff6b35"></path>
                    <circle cx="13" cy="15" r="5" fill="white"></circle>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                  <h3>Global Partners Solutions</h3>
                  <p>We provide comprehensive support for international partners entering Vietnam — from strategy and partnerships to growth and monetization.
(End-to-end advisory, operation & expansion services.)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="list-items wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay=".5s">
                <div class="icon">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="30" viewBox="0 0 26 30" fill="none">
                    <path d="M10.7219 1.19299C11.9737 0.456639 13.5263 0.456638 14.7781 1.19299L23.5281 6.34005C24.7498 7.05873 25.5 8.37033 25.5 9.78778V20.2122C25.5 21.6297 24.7498 22.9413 23.5281 23.66L14.7781 28.807C13.5263 29.5434 11.9737 29.5434 10.7219 28.807L1.97192 23.66C0.750167 22.9413 0 21.6297 0 20.2122V9.78778C0 8.37033 0.750165 7.05873 1.97192 6.34005L10.7219 1.19299Z" fill="#ff6b35"></path>
                    <circle cx="13" cy="15" r="5" fill="white"></circle>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div class="content">
                  <h3>Local Partners Network</h3>
                  <p>We collaborate with leading platforms such as Appmagic (exclusive in Vietnam), Yango Ads, and Playable Labs to empower local success.
(Driving innovation through strategic local alliances.)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .what-we-do-section {
    position: relative;
  }

  .left-shape-image {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    z-index: 1;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .left-shape-image img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1199px) {
    .left-shape-image {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>

